    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a budget-friendly commuter or a project car. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the passenger side door, and some fading paint on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all electronics and the air conditioning remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, honest car for the price.",
